from the Hong Kong pier.

380
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:03,690
Then hurry upstairs and send the message.

381
00:20:03,690 --> 00:20:04,880
Don't worry, Xian.

382
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:08,490
The bomber squadron
is already on standby at the airport.

383
00:20:08,490 --> 00:20:10,280
None of them will escape.

384
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:10,950
Ping,

385
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:12,150
