401
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:02,020
boom, had been blown to bits!

402
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,840
Win via Draw after Kong with Four Kongs!

403
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:09,670
Isn't that a big hand?

404
00:21:12,900 --> 00:21:13,950
It's beautiful.

405
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:17,110
Yes.

406
00:21:20,540 --> 00:21:21,230
Yinwan.

407
00:21:21,250 --> 00:21:21,820
Yes?

408
00:21:22,050 --> 00:21:23,370
When the war is over,

409
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:26,280
what are your plans for the future?

410
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,260
I've thought about it,

411
00:21:28,730 --> 00:21:30,190
but I haven't decided yet.

412
00:21:30,450 --> 00:21:31,510
But I have.

413
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:34,090
After all this is over,

414
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:36,650
I'll resign from the government

415
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:38,100
and sell Bachongtian Club.

416
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:38,730
Why?

417
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:42,280
You've stayed at Bachongtian Club

418
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:44,610
because you have something you want to do.

419
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,060
I've always known

420
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:48,420
that you long for a pure stage.

421
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:49,690
Your violin

422
00:21:49,910 --> 00:21:51,350
should be played for those

423
00:21:51,350 --> 00:21:53,400
who truly appreciate music.

424
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:58,500
I'm so tired after all these years.

425
00:21:59,050 --> 00:22:00,810
I want to leave all these disputes behind

426
00:22:00,810 --> 00:22:02,280
and fulfill my dream

427
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:04,080
to establish

428
00:22:04,110 --> 00:22:04,940
a genuine,

429
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,910
pure orchestra

430
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:08,750
and return to the original purpose
of music.

431
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:09,810
That's wonderful.

432
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:13,360
Yinwan.

433
00:22:13,390 --> 00:22:13,830
Yes?

434
00:22:15,330 --> 00:22:17,190
Will you do this with me?

435
00:22:21,310 --> 00:22:22,780
In this war,

436
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:26,560
many children have lost their families
and homes.

437
00:22:27,650 --> 00:22:29,550
After the war ends,

438
00:22:29,630 --> 00:22:30,900
I should return to the orphanage

439
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:31,870
to help those children

440
00:22:31,870 --> 00:22:33,800
find hope in their lives again.

441
00:22:36,180 --> 00:22:36,910
Well then...

442
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,440
Then I'll go with you.

443
00:22:40,490 --> 00:22:41,530
Whatever you do,

444
00:22:41,980 --> 00:22:43,060
I'll support you.

445
00:22:50,980 --> 00:22:51,950
Dr. Lok Pak.

446
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:54,190
Actually, I think

447
00:22:55,940 --> 00:22:56,660
you should do

448
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:58,230
what you truly want to do.

449
00:22:58,720 --> 00:22:59,120
I...

450
00:23:23,820 --> 00:23:27,600
[Chengxin Company Order]

451
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:32,360
Getting so much cargo this time.

452
00:23:35,700 --> 00:23:37,200
When I first got the order,

453
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,430
I didn't expect the quantity
to be so large.

454
00:23:39,430 --> 00:23:42,100
Mr. He and Mr. Ke's appetite

455
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:43,780
is getting bigger and bigger.

456
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:46,330
It's not about my appetite.

457
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:48,040
The war situation is developing rapidly,

458
00:23:48,040 --> 00:23:49,640
and domestic demand is high.

459
00:23:49,730 --> 00:23:51,680
Ever since the bombers
from Zhijiang Airport

460
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,890
could fly directly
to the Japanese homeland

461
00:23:53,890 --> 00:23:56,130
and drop bombs on their Imperial Palace,

462
00:23:56,130 --> 00:23:57,990
the Japanese have been panicked.

463
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,250
Yang Chang's intelligence station

464
00:23:59,250 --> 00:24:01,040
has also received notice from above.

465
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:02,000
They say the Japanese

466
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:03,830
are desperately moving troops,

467
00:24:03,850 --> 00:24:06,580
preparing for a large-scale attack
on Zhijiang.

468
00:24:06,940 --> 00:24:09,840
Hundreds of thousands of national troops
are preparing to meet them head-on.

469
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:13,240
The battle line is already far from
the Yunnan-Guizhou rear.

470
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:14,410
Once the battle begins,

471
00:24:14,410 --> 00:24:16,650
relying on the Burma Road and the Hump

472
00:24:16,670 --> 00:24:18,800
for limited supplies won't be enough.

473
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:20,180
So,

474
00:24:20,210 --> 00:24:22,230
the supplies coming through Macau
this time

475
00:24:22,230 --> 00:24:23,690
are more than ever before.

476
00:24:23,710 --> 00:24:24,510
That's right.

477
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:25,820
And in North and Central China,

478
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:27,370
taking advantage
of the enemy's vulnerable rear,

479
00:24:27,370 --> 00:24:28,820
the Eighth Route Army
and the New Fourth Army

480
00:24:28,820 --> 00:24:30,970
are also about to launch
a full counteroffensive.

481
00:24:30,970 --> 00:24:32,180
The supply gap is significant,

482
00:24:32,180 --> 00:24:33,780
so we've asked Mr. Rodrigues

483
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,030
to help with the procurement.

484
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:36,010
Excellent.

485
00:24:36,460 --> 00:24:37,900
The day we have long awaited—

486
00:24:37,900 --> 00:24:40,430
the counteroffensive—has finally arrived.

487
00:24:40,770 --> 00:24:43,440
I think the goods
will arrive in a day or two.

488
00:24:43,830 --> 00:24:46,000
You'll need to prepare more manpower;

489
00:24:46,170 --> 00:24:47,600
otherwise,

490
00:24:48,020 --> 00:24:49,810
I won't be able to unload everything.

491
00:24:49,810 --> 00:24:51,330
Luo, don't worry.

492
00:24:51,670 --> 00:24:52,920
However many people you need,

493
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,640
I'll send them to you.

494
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,360
Good.

495
00:24:55,490 --> 00:24:56,140
Also,

496
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:58,160
the Japanese anti-smuggling rights
in Macau

497
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,290
have been canceled,

498
00:24:59,290 --> 00:25:01,690
but this shipment is extremely important.

499
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:02,900
Better safe than sorry.

500
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:04,020
So when the time comes,

501
00:25:04,020 --> 00:25:05,220
we'll all keep watch at the pier.

502
00:25:05,220 --> 00:25:05,650
Yeah.

503
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:06,360
Sure.

504
00:25:06,670 --> 00:25:08,640
I'll have Gonçalves
send more Portuguese police

505
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:10,190
and find a reason to secure the pier

506
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:12,320
to ensure the safety of this shipment.

507
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:22,610
This is also it.

508
00:25:40,820 --> 00:25:41,980
Mr. Fukue!

509
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:44,600
Look at these.

510
00:25:46,340 --> 00:25:48,010
I've gathered all the investigation
and surveillance information

511
00:25:48,010 --> 00:25:50,320
about anti-Japanese forces in Macau

512
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:54,220
from the past 3 years!

513
00:25:55,550 --> 00:25:57,340
I plan to compile

514
00:25:57,370 --> 00:25:58,970
a detailed analysis report,

515
00:25:59,130 --> 00:26:02,810
along with new recommendations
for Macau operations,

516
00:26:03,210 --> 00:26:05,470
to submit to Command as soon as possible.

517
00:26:06,870 --> 00:26:09,050
New recommendations for Macau operations?

518
00:26:09,050 --> 00:26:10,380
What recommendations?

519
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:14,310
Of course, the armed occupation of Macau.

520
00:26:14,740 --> 00:26:16,140
What else could it be?

521
00:26:17,820 --> 00:26:18,640
Mr. Fukue.

522
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:22,690
You know everything that's happened
these past 3 years.

523
00:26:23,110 --> 00:26:24,800
The entire Macau

524
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:27,200
has been completely controlled by He Xian

525
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:29,140
and anti-Japanese elements.

526
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:32,300
The Anglo-American forces
have established contact with them,

527
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:35,820
and the Portuguese Macau government
has joined their camp.

528
00:26:36,750 --> 00:26:40,170
If the Imperial Army deploys immediately
to occupy Macau,

529
00:26:40,900 --> 00:26:46,420
the Macau issue
can be completely resolved!

530
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:50,490
Then why did you ask me to come?

531
00:26:51,770 --> 00:26:55,500
I want you to jointly submit
this proposal with me.

532
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:59,210
General Matsui is very displeased with me

533
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:02,960
and doesn't agree with
the military occupation strategy.

534
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:07,180
I alone can't convince Command.

535
00:27:15,630 --> 00:27:16,280
Why?

536
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,740
You don't want to co-sign?

537
00:27:22,470 --> 00:27:23,760
Well then,

538
00:27:24,710 --> 00:27:26,840
you can take the lead in submitting it,

539
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:28,740
and I'll co-sign. That works too.

540
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:32,180
It seems I do need to submit

541
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:35,500
a formal written proposal to Command.

542
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:38,360
That's more like it.

543
00:27:38,630 --> 00:27:40,630
I'll draft the report immediately.

544
00:27:41,370 --> 00:27:42,810
You'll just need to sign it.

545
00:27:42,810 --> 00:27:44,430
I'm submitting it myself,

546
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:46,980
not jointly with you.

547
00:27:48,690 --> 00:27:50,140
Not jointly with me?

548
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:54,320
Then what do you

549
00:27:55,370 --> 00:27:57,160
plan to recommend?

550
00:27:58,140 --> 00:27:59,540
I recommend that Command

551
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:03,390
