to occupy Macau!

573
00:29:22,850 --> 00:29:28,610
Your insane ideas

574
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:32,750
have seriously jeopardized
the Empire's Sacred War.

575
00:29:33,140 --> 00:29:36,570
As the Consul in Macau,

576
00:29:37,090 --> 00:29:41,420
I must take responsibility
for the Empire's interests.

577
00:29:42,090 --> 00:29:42,750
Therefore,

578
00:29:43,750 --> 00:29:45,750
I will submit a report to Command,

579
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:49,750
