with comprehensive documentation.

581
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:56,750
I believe that once Command
receives my report,

582
00:29:57,240 --> 00:30:01,070
they'll take appropriate action
against Sawa Agency.

583
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:27,490
Great. The goods have finally arrived.

