Since they started unloading,

596
00:31:09,620 --> 00:31:12,690
the Portuguese police have completely
sealed off the entire port.

597
00:31:12,690 --> 00:31:14,020
Nobody is allowed near.

598
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,030
But the people unloading

599
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,640
