from the Tai Ho Brotherhood.

600
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:18,630
Our people simply can't get close.

601
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:19,460
Also,

602
00:31:20,150 --> 00:31:21,900
He Xian and his people were there too.

603
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:23,950
They kept watch for 2 whole days

604
00:31:23,970 --> 00:31:25,230
while they were unloading the cargo.

605
00:31:25,230 --> 00:31:26,700
They didn't leave

606
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:29,400
until all the goods were placed

607
00:31:29,430 --> 00:31:30,890
in Rodrigues' warehouse.

608
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:34,870
Chief,

609
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:38,280
according to Captain Huang's report,

610
00:31:38,430 --> 00:31:40,650
the underground anti-Japanese forces
in Macau

611
00:31:40,650 --> 00:31:43,250
are organizing the transport
of new supplies,

612
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:46,100
and the quantity is unprecedented.

613
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:49,000
What do you think we should do?

614
00:31:59,110 --> 00:32:00,110
Major Yamaguchi,

615
